## ✊🏾 **Major Contributions of Black-Owned Banks & Financial Institutions**

### **1️⃣ Funding Black Homeownership & Business Ownership**

- Black-owned banks provided **mortgages and business loans** when white-owned banks denied Black applicants due to **redlining**.
- Example: **OneUnited Bank** finances small businesses in urban Black communities.

