## ⚖️ **Challenges & Future of Black-Owned Banks**

⚠️ **Declining Black-Owned Banks** – There were over **100 Black-owned banks in the 1960s**; today, fewer than **20 remain**.  
⚠️ **Systemic Banking Discrimination** – **Redlining, predatory lending, and racial credit scoring gaps persist**.  
⚠️ **Lack of Capital Investment** – Black banks struggle to compete with larger financial institutions due to **lower capital reserves**.  
⚠️ **Digital Disruption** – **Big banks and fintech firms** increasingly dominate online banking, challenging traditional Black-owned banks.

🔗 **Possible Solutions:**

- **Investing in Black-Owned Banks** 💰
- **Expanding Fintech & Digital Banking for Black Communities** 📱
